text: I have my own terminal https://cogno.rocks and I'm thinking about integrating ChatGPT or a similar technology directly into the terminal. The task doesn't seem too difficult. At least using the ChatGPT API. I don't have much experience with it yet. Have you ever used an AI to search for terminal commands? Would it be helpful for you or do you have any concerns?
